snippet.title: Pick me Pick me - Launch trailer
snippet.description:
Pick Me Pick Me will be available on Oct 24. 2024 👉​ https://store.steampowered.com/app/3189430/Pick_Me_Pick_Me/

Engage in "Pick Me Pick Me," the ultimate 2-player online showdown where you battle it out in the Battlefield of Love. Use your creative ideas to start an interesting conversation with the characters powered by AI, and place strategic cards to out-charm your rival in hilarious dating scenarios.

Pick Me Pick Me is an online 2-player versus game : https://www.pickmepickme.ai/

Brush off your smoothest pick up lines and show off just how charming you can be!

Follow us on social medias for more info:
https://discord.gg/pickmepickme
https://x.com/PickmePickmeAi
https://www.instagram.com/pickmepickmeai/
